In the INTEREST OF D.C., Minor Child, D.C., Minor Child, Appellant. No. 18-0976 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

D.C. appeals from the dispositional orders placing him in the custody of Juvenile Court Services for placement in residential treatment foster care. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
